EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName} {!Contact.LastName},
Go here to unsubscribe from all emails from our organization. https://INSERTYOURSITEDOMAINHERE/Unsubscribe?recordId={!Contact.Id}&Email={!Contact.Email}
Instructions: Change INSERTYOURSITEDOMAINHERE to the site domain you created earlier. Delete the instructions here and add the rest of your email above the link. Notes: This email template comes with the unmanaged package "Unsubscribe Link." The link will launch the Unsubscribe Link flow. The flow will have an error if an email address includes a special character like +. The package contains a visualforce email template that accommodates special characters. Better yet, use lightning templates and the Unsubscribe Link formula fields.
